OL,3,CGuernsey woman charged for attempting
OL,4,Cto murder her mother
OL,6,FA Guernsey woman has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt, charged with attempting to
OL,8,Fmurder her mother.
OL,10,FShakira Naftel, aged 20, appeared in
OL,11,FGuernsey's Magistrates Court on
OL,12,FTuesday 28 April.
OL,14,FShe will be remanded in police custody
OL,15,Fwhile investigations proceed.
OL,17,FGuernsey Police were previously called
OL,18,Fto a house on Victoria Avenue in St
OL,19,FSampson in the early hours of Sunday
OL,20,Fmorning (26th April).
