OL,3,CGuernsey woman charged for attempting
OL,4,Cto murder her mother
OL,6,FAt the time, Naftel was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder, while
OL,8,Fher mother was urgently transferred to
OL,9,FPrincess Elizabeth Hospital with
OL,10,F"severe abdominal injuries".
OL,12,FNaftel will appear again in court for
OL,13,Fa review hearing on 26 May 2026.
